    • Method Detail

      • isKbpPronominalMention

        public static boolean isKbpPronominalMention(String word)
        Returns whether the given token counts as a valid pronominal mention for KBP. This method (at present) works for either Chinese or English.
        Parameters:
        word - The token to classify.
        Returns:
        true if this token is a pronoun that KBP should recognize (3rd person, non-neuter, non reflexive).
